[36.349889, "o", "\u001b[1;35;40mYou have a series of scheduled events coming up:\r\n\r\n1. **Team Meeting** on July 10, 2025, from 9:00 AM to 10:00 AM at Conference Room A to discuss project progress.\r\n\r\n2. **Client Presentation** on July 11, 2025, from 2:00 PM to 3:00 PM in Meeting Room 2 for presenting new campaign ideas.\r\n\r\n3. **Weekly Check-In** on July 13, 2025, from 4:00 PM to 5:00 PM via Zoom for a team check-up.\r\n\r\n4. **Project Deadline** on July 15, 2025, from 12:00 PM to 1:00 PM at the office to submit final project deliverables.\r\n\r\n5. **Networking Lunch** on July 16, 2025, from 12:30 PM to 1:30 PM at Downtown Cafe for lunch with industry peers.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[37.680081, "o", "\u001b[93mPlanner: User: The calendar has several events scheduled around mid-July. The existing events occur on July 10th, 11th, 13th, 15th, and 16th. How many days do you plan for the cruise, and would you like me to find options outside of these dates or only on open days without events?\u001b[0m\r\n"]
