[84.70549, "o", "\u001b[1;35;40mThe API query for available cruises departing from Seattle on July 5th, 2025, returned three options:\r\n\r\n1. **Alaska Explorer**:\r\n   - Cabin Type: Inside\r\n   - Price: $750 per person\r\n   - Availability: Yes\r\n\r\n2. **Glacier Adventure**:\r\n   - Cabin Type: Oceanview\r\n   - Price: $950 per person\r\n   - Availability: Yes\r\n\r\n3. **Pacific Northwest Dream**:\r\n   - Cabin Type: Balcony\r\n   - Price: $1200 per person\r\n   - Availability: Yes\r\n\r\nAll options are available for a 5-day journey returning on July 10th, 2025.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[88.923407, "o", "\u001b[93mPlanner: User: The available cruise options to Alaska starting on July 5th and returning on July 10th are as follows:\r\n\r\n1. Alaska Explorer - Inside Cabin: $750 per person\r\n2. Glacier Adventure - Oceanview Cabin: $950 per person\r\n3. Pacific Northwest Dream - Balcony Cabin: $1200 per person\r\n\r\nWould you like to proceed with booking any of these options and place it on your calendar, or do you have any other preferences?\u001b[0m\r\n"]
